The South African Chamber of Commerce
and Industry releases its Trade Conditions Survey for January at
11:30 a.m. in Johannesburg. An improvement in the measure since
September, excluding the seasonal slowdown in Christmas, will
probably continue, the chamber said last month.  To contact the reporter on this story:
